SUMMARY:Sweat Fest 2026 - Movement Is Ours
DESCRIPTION:Latina Sweat Project's first-ever all-day movement festival in
 Chicago. A celebration of wellness\, cultura\, and connection.\n\nRUN OF
 SHOW\n7:00 to 8:30 AM - RUN: Kickoff 5K with all paces welcome. Walk it\,
 jog it\, or chase a PR.\n9:00 AM to 5:00 PM - SWEAT: 45-minute classes
 throughout the day with LSP instructors.\n6:00 to 9:00 PM - PACHANGA:
 Dance\, connect\, and celebrate with your comunidad until the final
 set.\n\nThroughout the day: wellbeing experiences\, local
 vendors\, food and drink\,
 and community connection. All levels are welcome.\n\nTickets are on sale
 soon. Plan your day and get updates at
 https://latinasweatproject.com/sweatfest\nPartnership inquiries:
 rut@latinasweatproject.com
